hers give thanks without smiles, Keth smiles like a cut and asks only for a future conversation, and Sere walks away with the rope’s hum in her hands and a quiet chain in her wake.\"\n      ],\n      \"connections\": {\"previous\": [\"6\", \"7\", \"9\", \"10\"], \"next\": [\"12\"]},\n      \"rewards\": [\n        {\"type\": \"City State\", \"description\": \"The chain quiets and the Heartward Engine’s pulse settles two measures toward sleep, granting Marrowgate a deeper calm and fewer panic-songs in the ribs.\"},\n        {\"type\": \"Item\", \"description\": \"A length of storm-tempered rope that hums softly when pressure shifts dangerously, warning of sudden gusts, treacherous waves, or a chain ready to sing again.\"},\n        {\"type\": \"Renown\", \"description\": \"Esteem across guilds as the climber who taught the sky a lullaby, opening doors among Pilots, Tidemothers, Bonewrights, and even grudging Wardens.\"}\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"